{"tid":2185882,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個日式料理食譜分享","createTime":"2020-09-02T14:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T19:43:59.000Z","uid":199985,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"425aba9f5bf1bebca4cf3f84513323ce52488eef","tid":2185882,"uid":199985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n厚切方包 1塊<br />\n大紅蘋果 1/4個<br />\n蜜糖 適量<br />\n牛油，<br />\n肉桂粉適量<br />\n1.蘋果洗好，平均厚度切薄片。  <br />\n2.牛油塗上方包後，再塗上少量蜜糖<br />\n3.把蘋果片一正一反地左右疊上方包上（擺法可參考上圖）<br />\n4.把蘋果包放上焗盆，焗160度5分鐘<br />\n5.蘋果微乾變黃就得<br />\n6.拎出吐司，蘋果面上再塗一層蜜糖用上火焗180度焗2-3分鐘。 製作完成，灑d肉桂粉裝飾調味"},{"pid":"1d8ba4e2ca96e609776ac3adaedc8af034d94c0f","tid":2185882,"uid":373442,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T14:46:08.000Z","msg":"你呢個算係日式<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96572158933500f15dff994840b09c961fd58579","tid":2185882,"uid":215475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T19:29:25.000Z","msg":"上圖喺邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9d58f51c8effe4b16034ff6a7893298abac71a","tid":2185882,"uid":346854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T19:33:42.000Z","msg":"有冇圖"},{"pid":"45d6a6a4333a3c86e7f1ee9feb26dca722dc78f5","tid":2185882,"uid":168619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T19:42:41.000Z","msg":"百佳買嘅即食日式咖哩加飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97cf8a51a170e63b9a0451b2f89ef546e34e1c1","tid":2185882,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T19:43:59.000Z","msg":"1. 整舊飯 <br />\n2. 切塊魚擺上去"}]}